        "description": "RoomSketcher is the easiest way to create, edit, and visualize detailed 2D and 3D floor plans.",
        "longDescription": "RoomSketcher is an innovative technology company that offers a user-friendly floor plan and home design software. With our powerful yet easy-to-use RoomSketcher App, you can create stunning floor plans, furnish and decorate them, and visualize in impressive 3D. Join our community of floor plan and home design enthusiasts, including real estate professionals, interior design enthusiasts, homeowners, and more. Our journey began in 2007 when RoomSketcher was founded as a spin-off from a company specializing in 3D visualizations for the sub-sea oil industry. We adapted the same technology to visualize the interior of homes and properties, making it accessible to everyone online. Our unique One Source platform enables instant access to a wide range of premium output possibilities, including professional 2D and 3D Floor Plans, Live 3D, 3D Photos, and 360 Views. Backed by Argentum and the holding company Torrey Pins AS, RoomSketcher has grown to serve over five million users and customers in over 170 countries. Join us and experience the best floor plan and home design tool on the market. Get started today!.",
